{"abstract":[{"text":"You will often find the type ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Variant"},{"type":"text","text":" in Godot source code.   Variants are"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Godot’s way of passing around certain data types.  They are similar to Swift’s","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Any"},{"type":"text","text":" type, but they can only hold Godot types (most structures and classes"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"that derive from ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/GodotObject"},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot"]]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/Variant","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"topicSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/Variant\/==(_:_:)"],"title":"Operators"},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/Variant\/init()","doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/Variant\/init(_:)-17via","doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/Variant\/init(_:)-1hl8w","doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/Variant\/init(_:)-1ib32","doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/Variant\/init(_:)-1jzkb","doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/Variant\/init(_:)-27wm0","doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/Variant\/init(_:)-2jijg","doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/Variant\/init(_:)-2nvmw","doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/Variant\/init(_:)-2wce3","doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/Variant\/init(_:)-2xwk8","doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/Variant\/init(_:)-3251m","doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/Variant\/init(_:)-35yqb","doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/Variant\/init(_:)-3i5kd","doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/Variant\/init(_:)-3l1tn","